<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","level":1,"align":"wide","className":"founders-hero-title","style":{"color":{"text":"var(\u002d\u002dwp\u002d\u002dpreset\u002d\u002dcolor\u002d\u002dc-gold)"},"typography":{"fontFamily":"var(\u002d\u002dwp\u002d\u002dpreset\u002d\u002dfont-family\u002d\u002dcinzel-decorative)"}}} -->
<h1 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-center founders-hero-title has-text-color" style="color:var(--wp--preset--color--c-gold);font-family:var(--wp--preset--font-family--cinzel-decorative)">About Veils</h1>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"className":"has-text-align-center world-intro","style":{"typography":{"textAlign":"center"},"color":{"text":"#ffffff"}},"fontSize":"xl","fontFamily":"cormorant-garamond"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center world-intro has-text-color has-cormorant-garamond-font-family has-xl-font-size" style="color:#ffffff"><em>Create your hero. Shape the story. Uncover what the founders left behind.</em></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:group {"metadata":{"name":"Founders Hero Divider"},"className":"founders-hero-divider","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group founders-hero-divider"><!-- wp:group {"metadata":{"name":"Hero Diamond [Decorative]"},"className":"founders-hero-diamond miles-editor-hidden"} -->
<div class="wp-block-group founders-hero-diamond miles-editor-hidden"></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></section>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:group {"tagName":"section","metadata":{"name":"Founders Narrative Section"},"align":"full","className":"founders-narrative","style":{"color":{"background":"var(\u002d\u002dwp\u002d\u002dpreset\u002d\u002dcolor\u002d\u002dc-stone)"}},"layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<section class="wp-block-group alignfull founders-narrative has-background" style="background-color:var(--wp--preset--color--c-stone)"><!-- wp:group {"metadata":{"name":"Founders Narrative Inner"},"className":"founders-narrative-inner","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group founders-narrative-inner"><!-- wp:columns {"style":{"spacing":{"blockGap":{"left":"var:preset|spacing|50"}}}} -->
<div class="wp-block-columns"><!-- wp:column -->
<div class="wp-block-column"><!-- wp:heading {"className":"founders-lore-title animate-on-scroll","style":{"typography":{"fontFamily":"var(\u002d\u002dfont-heading)","fontSize":"clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem)"},"color":{"text":"#C9A84C"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading founders-lore-title animate-on-scroll has-text-color" style="color:#C9A84C;font-family:var(--font-heading);font-size:clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem)">The Story</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"className":"founders-lore-text","style":{"color":{"text":"var(\u002d\u002dwp\u002d\u002dpreset\u002d\u002dcolor\u002d\u002dc-bone)"}},"fontSize":"lg"} -->
<p class="founders-lore-text has-text-color has-lg-font-size" style="color:var(--wp--preset--color--c-bone)">In the age before history was written, when the world still trembled with raw creation, four extraordinary souls discovered something that would change the course of existence forever. Deep within the Whispering Caverns — where reality grew thin and the boundaries between worlds dissolved like morning frost — they found the Amethyst Veil: a gem of impossible beauty that pulsed with the heartbeat of forgotten gods.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"className":"founders-lore-text","style":{"color":{"text":"var(\u002d\u002dwp\u002d\u002dpreset\u002d\u002dcolor\u002d\u002dc-bone)"},"spacing":{"padding":{"top":"var:preset|spacing|40"}}},"fontSize":"lg"} -->
<p class="founders-lore-text has-text-color has-lg-font-size" style="color:var(--wp--preset--color--c-bone);padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40)">For generations, the people of Eldermoor have whispered their names with reverence and dread in equal measure. Seraphine the Wise, whose sight pierced the veils of time. Aldric the Golden, whose blade carved order from chaos. Thornwen the Green, whose roots held the world together. And Varek the Shieldborn, whose ambition would one day crack the very foundations they had built.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column -->
<div class="wp-block-column"><!-- wp:heading {"className":"founders-lore-title animate-on-scroll","style":{"typography":{"fontFamily":"var(\u002d\u002dfont-heading)","fontSize":"clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem)"},"color":{"text":"#C9A84C"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading founders-lore-title animate-on-scroll has-text-color" style="color:#C9A84C;font-family:var(--font-heading);font-size:clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem)">Gameplay</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"className":"founders-lore-text","style":{"color":{"text":"var(\u002d\u002dwp\u002d\u002dpreset\u002d\u002dcolor\u002d\u002dc-bone)"}},"fontSize":"lg"} -->
<p class="founders-lore-text has-text-color has-lg-font-size" style="color:var(--wp--preset--color--c-bone)">Tales of Eldermoor is a text-based RPG built on a simple truth: the best stories are the ones you shape yourself.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"className":"founders-lore-text","style":{"color":{"text":"var(\u002d\u002dwp\u002d\u002dpreset\u002d\u002dcolor\u002d\u002dc-bone)"},"spacing":{"padding":{"top":"var:preset|spacing|40"}}},"fontSize":"lg"} -->
<p class="founders-lore-text has-text-color has-lg-font-size" style="color:var(--wp--preset--color--c-bone);padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40)">Every scene is a decision. Every decision has weight. There are no throwaway choices here — the path you take closes doors behind you, opens others you didn't expect, and remembers everything. Alliances forged and enemies made, words spoken in haste, mercy shown or withheld — the world of Eldermoor pays attention.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"className":"founders-lore-text","style":{"color":{"text":"var(\u002d\u002dwp\u002d\u002dpreset\u002d\u002dcolor\u002d\u002dc-bone)"},"spacing":{"padding":{"top":"var:preset|spacing|40"}}},"fontSize":"lg"} -->
<p class="founders-lore-text has-text-color has-lg-font-size" style="color:var(--wp--preset--color--c-bone);padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40)">You don't need a controller. You don't need an install. You need a browser and the willingness to see where the story takes you.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:column --></div>
<!-- /wp:columns --></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></section>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:group {"metadata":{"name":"Founders Bios","categories":["veils-patterns"],"patternName":"miles-veils-of-fate-tales-of-eldermoor-fc13d6a3/character-bio-content-left"},"align":"full","className":"founders-bios","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignfull founders-bios"><!-- wp:group {"tagName":"section","metadata":{"name":"Founder Seraphine Section"},"className":"founder-section founder-section\u002d\u002dvoid founder-seraphine","style":{"color":{"background":"#0a0612"}},"layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<section class="wp-block-group founder-section founder-section--void founder-seraphine has-background" style="background-color:#0a0612"><!-- wp:group {"metadata":{"name":"Seraphine Inner"},"className":"founder-inner founder-inner\u002d\u002dimg-right","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group founder-inner founder-inner--img-right"><!-- wp:group {"metadata":{"name":"Seraphine Text"},"className":"founder-text","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group founder-text"><!-- wp:heading {"className":"founder-name animate-on-scroll","style":{"typography":{"fontFamily":"var(\u002d\u002dfont-heading)","fontSize":"clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem)"},"color":{"text":"#C9A84C"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading founder-name animate-on-scroll has-text-color" style="color:#C9A84C;font-family:var(--font-heading);font-size:clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem)">Your Choices Matter</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"className":"founder-lore animate-on-scroll","style":{"color":{"text":"#d4c9b8"}},"fontSize":"lg"} -->
<p class="founder-lore animate-on-scroll has-text-color has-lg-font-size" style="color:#d4c9b8">This isn't a story that happens to you. It's a story you build.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"className":"founder-lore animate-on-scroll","style":{"color":{"text":"#d4c9b8"}},"fontSize":"lg"} -->
<p class="founder-lore animate-on-scroll has-text-color has-lg-font-size" style="color:#d4c9b8">Branching storylines stretch across multiple campaigns, each shaped by the sum of your decisions. Hidden scenes surface only for those who look carefully — or choose boldly. Secret paths open to characters with the right stats, the right reputation, the right history. What one hero discovers, another may never find.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"className":"founder-lore animate-on-scroll","style":{"color":{"text":"#d4c9b8"}},"fontSize":"lg"} -->
<p class="founder-lore animate-on-scroll has-text-color has-lg-font-size" style="color:#d4c9b8">Your actions have consequences that echo. A favour done in chapter one may save your life in chapter three. A betrayal you thought you'd buried has a way of resurfacing.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"className":"founder-lore animate-on-scroll","style":{"color":{"text":"#d4c9b8"}},"fontSize":"lg"} -->
<p class="founder-lore animate-on-scroll has-text-color has-lg-font-size" style="color:#d4c9b8">Play it again as someone else and you'll barely recognize the story.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:group {"metadata":{"name":"Seraphine Portrait Wrap"},"className":"founder-portrait-wrap animate-from-right animate-on-scroll","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group founder-portrait-wrap animate-from-right animate-on-scroll"><!-- wp:image {"sizeSlug":"full","className":"founder-portrait"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-full founder-portrait"><img src="http://localhost:8895/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/founder-seraphine.jpg" alt="Seraphine the Wise — a mystical sage with silver-white hair and violet-amber eyes, wearing flowing dark robes with golden embroidery"/></figure>
<!-- /wp:image --></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></section>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

